<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8308593>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Species of Drimia Jacq. ex Willd. 1. Drimia ciliaris Jacq. ex Willd. from Jacquin (1795: tab. 377); 2. Drimia elata Jacq. ex Willd. from Jacquin (1794: tab. 373); 3. Drimia media Jacq. ex Willd. from Jacquin (1795: tab. 375); 4. Drimia pusilla Jacq. ex Willd. from Jacquin (1794: tab. 374)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8308593/files/figure.png" ;
