<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8308595>
    dc:description "FIGURE 19. Species of Drimia Jacq. ex Willd. 1. Drimia alta R.A.Dyer from Hooker (1865: t. 5522 as Drimia altissima Hook.f.); 2. Drimia alta R.A.Dyer from Dyer (1943: t. 890); 3. Drimia robusta Baker from Baker (1870b: t. 190); 4. Drimia villosa Lindl. from Lindley (1830: t. 1346)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8308595/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8308597>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Species of Drimia Jacq. ex Willd. displayed in horizontal rows of images. 1. Drimia elata Jacq. ex Willd.; 2. Drimia haworthioides Baker; 3. Drimia neriniformis Baker; 4. Drimia robusta Baker; 5. Drimia sphaerocephala Baker." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8308597/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

